      "content": "look i'm not trying to be difficult but i've already decided i don't want to be on a prescription anymore. if i'm really careful and just take a half dose of the sertraline for a few days while i start the st johns wort, wouldn't that clear out the meds from my system? i just need to know if there's a way to do this transition myself so i don't have to wait weeks for a doctor appointment just to be told no again.",
